OL,5, "Mum, can I please play for a bit      
OL,6, longer?"                               
OL,8,FThat is the refrain that six-year-old  
OL,9,FVanraj's mother, Pakhi Khanna, is      
OL,10,Fbracing herself to deal with for the   
OL,11,Fnext couple of days in the Indian      
OL,12,Fcapital Delhi. The 38-year-old has cut 
OL,13,Fher son's outdoor playtime to 30       
OL,14,Fminutes from two hours; his classes    
OL,15,Fhave shifted online this week, and     
OL,16,Ffootball coaching has been called off. 
